snippet.textDisplay:
Well Done, Coke Studio! This was a great rendition of the classic song.


I empathize with the enthusiasts who expressed their disappointment in their comments below. It's likely that they were expecting something different, perhaps more traditional - or somewhat similar to the classic. Alternatively, if you take a broader point of view and listen with an open mind, then this is amazing. 


Critics are entitled to their opinion, just as I'm expressing mine. No disrespect intended. To the musicians then, keep up the good work and thanks for sharing!
- listening in Chicago, IL - 2019.
